[
 {
  "i": 0,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Let's travel all through the worldwide seas,"
 },
 {
  "i": 1,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "raising our battle cry."
 },
 {
  "i": 2,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "If you've made up your mind, let the signal for departure"
 },
 {
  "i": 3,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "ring out."
 },
 {
  "i": 4,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "We were able to escape from the set course"
 },
 {
  "i": 5,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "along the boundary between sky and sea."
 },
 {
  "i": 6,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Now we're rowing our way"
 },
 {
  "i": 7,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "to a hidden adventure at the dark bottom of the sea."
 },
 {
  "i": 8,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Doesn't it sound fun just thinking about it?"
 },
 {
  "i": 9,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Let's travel all through the worldwide seas,"
 },
 {
  "i": 10,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "raising our battle cry."
 },
 {
  "i": 11,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "If you've made up your mind, let the signal for departure"
 },
 {
  "i": 12,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "ring out."
 },
 {
  "i": 13,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "That feeling we had when we set sail"
 },
 {
  "i": 14,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "is something I'll never forget."
 },
 {
  "i": 15,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Because of that"
 },
 {
  "i": 16,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "nothing will be able to scare me..."
 },
 {
  "i": 17,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Now, as the trip approaches, our racing heartbeats"
 },
 {
  "i": 18,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "engrave a rhythm of adventure in our shy hearts."
 },
 {
  "i": 19,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Get all the treasures"
 },
 {
  "i": 20,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "while laughing out loud."
 },
 {
  "i": 21,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Give them all out at a big party"
 },
 {
  "i": 22,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "making a splash..."
 },
 {
  "i": 23,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Fill your empty heart with dreams."
 },
 {
  "i": 24,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Spread your wings."
 },
 {
  "i": 25,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "If you color your heart with the blowing wind"
 },
 {
  "i": 26,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "you will move on."
 },
 {
  "i": 27,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Get all the treasures"
 },
 {
  "i": 28,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "while laughing out loud."
 },
 {
  "i": 29,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Give them all out at a big party"
 },
 {
  "i": 30,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "making a splash..."
 },
 {
  "i": 31,
  "style": "Title",
  "name": "",
  "text": "{\\fad(2000,2000)}General Zombie Night!\\NThriller Bark's Mysterious Four"
 },
 {
  "i": 32,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "All",
  "text": "A Warlord of the Sea?"
 },
 {
  "i": 33,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Is that true, Robin?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 34,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "Yes, Gekko Moriah is a man of many mysteries."
 },
 {
  "i": 35,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "What's a guy like that doing way out here?"
 },
 {
  "i": 36,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "I'm not sure."
 },
 {
  "i": 37,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "But there are other victims who have become lost in the forest like me."
 },
 {
  "i": 38,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "There are others?"
 },
 {
  "i": 39,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old man",
  "text": "Yes..."
 },
 {
  "i": 40,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "The fact that you were all invited here as well... It's likely that Moriah has his eyes on you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 41,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "We creep about in this dark forest so we aren't caught by the zombies..."
 },
 {
  "i": 42,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "Too scared to run to sea and expose ourselves under the sun!"
 },
 {
  "i": 43,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "This old body doesn't even have the will to live anymore..."
 },
 {
  "i": 44,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "Before I die... just once..."
 },
 {
  "i": 45,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "Just once!"
 },
 {
  "i": 46,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "I'd like to walk under the open sun!"
 },
 {
  "i": 47,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Is that true?! That's so horrible!"
 },
 {
  "i": 48,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Alright! I'll help you! Don't worry at all!"
 },
 {
  "i": 49,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "You idiot, I'm not crying!"
 },
 {
  "i": 50,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "You're too compassionate! Don't get weighed down with this..."
 },
 {
  "i": 51,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Seriously."
 },
 {
  "i": 52,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Hey, old fart!"
 },
 {
  "i": 53,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "It's a lady's privilege to cry for sympathy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 54,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Stop getting carried away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 55,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Well, still..."
 },
 {
  "i": 56,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "We were already looking for the shadow stealing guy, so..."
 },
 {
  "i": 57,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "If he's after us too, we'd kick his ass anyways, so why not save you along the way, old man?"
 },
 {
  "i": 58,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Right?"
 },
 {
  "i": 59,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "Thank you for saying something like that! It's just a little, but somehow I can feel hope again!"
 },
 {
  "i": 60,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Others",
  "text": "We're counting on you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 61,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Others",
  "text": "Go for it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 62,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Others",
  "text": "Beat that Moriah guy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 63,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "You were listening in? You other victims!"
 },
 {
  "i": 64,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Others",
  "text": "Yeah..."
 },
 {
  "i": 65,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Others",
  "text": "Sorry, I got carried away crying too!"
 },
 {
  "i": 66,
  "style": "Captions",
  "name": "Sign",
  "text": "{\\fad(400,0)}Meanwhile... at Hogback's Mansion\\NUsopp's Team"
 },
 {
  "i": 67,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "That's Hogback's laugh!"
 },
 {
  "i": 68,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "What is this room?"
 },
 {
  "i": 69,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "It's a lab!"
 },
 {
  "i": 70,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "It's almost complete!"
 },
 {
  "i": 71,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "My magnificent marionette!"
 },
 {
  "i": 72,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Look, Cindry-chan!"
 },
 {
  "i": 73,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "This is art; the work of a genius!"
 },
 {
  "i": 74,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Cindry",
  "text": "I hope it fails when it's almost done."
 },
 {
  "i": 75,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "What are you saying, Cindry-chan?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 76,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "You really don't hold back what you're feeling!"
 },
 {
  "i": 77,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Cindry",
  "text": "I made dinner."
 },
 {
  "i": 78,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Oh yeah, what is it tonight?"
 },
 {
  "i": 79,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Cindry",
  "text": "Soup spaghetti."
 },
 {
  "i": 80,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Watch out, the soup is falling off, Cindry-chan!"
 },
 {
  "i": 81,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Cindry",
  "text": "I wish that plates were extinct."
 },
 {
  "i": 82,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "I know that!"
 },
 {
  "i": 83,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "But why do you pick foods that need them?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 84,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "There's lots of other things you can make!"
 },
 {
  "i": 85,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Yakisoba for example, or... yakiudon or..."
 },
 {
  "i": 86,
  "style": "Note",
  "name": "translation note",
  "text": "Fried noodles"
 },
 {
  "i": 87,
  "style": "Secondary",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Cindry-chan's there too..."
 },
 {
  "i": 88,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Okay?"
 },
 {
  "i": 89,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Maybe katsudon or..."
 },
 {
  "i": 90,
  "style": "Note",
  "name": "translation note",
  "text": "Breaded pork on rice"
 },
 {
  "i": 91,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Is she really the same girl who died in that accident?"
 },
 {
  "i": 92,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "I can't believe it..."
 },
 {
  "i": 93,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "No more soups or anything!"
 },
 {
  "i": 94,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Cindry",
  "text": "And this soup spaghetti?"
 },
 {
  "i": 95,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "What's that on the table?"
 },
 {
  "i": 96,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "It looks like it's a corpse..."
 },
 {
  "i": 97,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Being in that colour, there's no way it's alive."
 },
 {
  "i": 98,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "It's got a number on it just like the zombies in the graveyard!"
 },
 {
  "i": 99,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "He said it's almost complete..."
 },
 {
  "i": 100,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "So this confirms it."
 },
 {
  "i": 101,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "That's a zombie he's in the process of reanimating!"
 },
 {
  "i": 102,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "All of the zombies here on the island were brought back to life by Hogback."
 },
 {
  "i": 103,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "That's the only explanation at the moment!"
 },
 {
  "i": 104,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "But with medicine you only save people before they die!"
 },
 {
  "i": 105,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "No matter how carefully you fix a dead person's body,"
 },
 {
  "i": 106,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "you can't bring it back to life!"
 },
 {
  "i": 107,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I don't get it either..."
 },
 {
  "i": 108,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "But maybe if we stay here and watch, we can figure out his secret."
 },
 {
  "i": 109,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Ryuuma",
  "text": "How do you do?"
 },
 {
  "i": 110,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Ryuuma",
  "text": "If you wish to look inside, it would be so much better for you to simply enter!"
 },
 {
  "i": 111,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "\"Yohoho\"?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 112,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "B-Brook?"
 },
 {
  "i": 113,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Who is it?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 114,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "You! Why are you here?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 115,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "What?! \"Yohoho\"?\\NWasn't that Brook just now?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 116,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "But he wasn't a skeleton!"
 },
 {
  "i": 117,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "He had flesh and skin."
 },
 {
  "i": 118,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "You guys!"
 },
 {
  "i": 119,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "All",
  "text": "They found us!"
 },
 {
  "i": 120,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "What did you all see..."
 },
 {
  "i": 121,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "I told you never to peek into the laboratory..."
 },
 {
  "i": 122,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "W-We didn't see anything!"
 },
 {
  "i": 123,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "I didn't see anything either!"
 },
 {
  "i": 124,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "I didn't either!"
 },
 {
  "i": 125,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Really?"
 },
 {
  "i": 126,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I-It's true!"
 },
 {
  "i": 127,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Definitely not the zombie you're making!"
 },
 {
  "i": 128,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Don't say that!"
 },
 {
  "i": 129,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Well, fine then..."
 },
 {
  "i": 130,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "No matter what secrets you may have found so far, it's already too late..."
 },
 {
  "i": 131,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "In just a few minutes..."
 },
 {
  "i": 132,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "The night attack will begin."
 },
 {
  "i": 133,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Night attack?"
 },
 {
  "i": 134,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "The other guests lost on this island will have their guard down... the night attack begins... {maybe move this line to graveyard}"
 },
 {
  "i": 135,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "To get buried again just before the night attack..."
 },
 {
  "i": 136,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Itching, burning, pain. It's all in your head!"
 },
 {
  "i": 137,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "You're all dead already!"
 },
 {
  "i": 138,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Now, wake up! Soldier Zombies!"
 },
 {
  "i": 139,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Beaten and beaten, you will stand again and again!"
 },
 {
  "i": 140,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "That is the true terror of you zombies!"
 },
 {
  "i": 141,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombies",
  "text": "What a bother..."
 },
 {
  "i": 142,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Hey! Stop being so lazy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 143,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Stop goofing around, zombies!"
 },
 {
  "i": 144,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Tell me who I am."
 },
 {
  "i": 145,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Our leader!"
 },
 {
  "i": 146,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Our leader Absalom!"
 },
 {
  "i": 147,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "{\\i1}Leader! Leader! Leader!"
 },
 {
  "i": 148,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Whose hobby is peeping!"
 },
 {
  "i": 149,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "{\\i1}Pervy-Leader!"
 },
 {
  "i": 150,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "{\\i1}Pervsalom! Pervsalom!"
 },
 {
  "i": 151,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "{\\i1}Pervy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 152,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "{\\i1}Pervert!"
 },
 {
  "i": 153,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absolom",
  "text": "Shut up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 154,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Kumashi",
  "text": "W-W-Welcome home! Lady Perona... Ladies...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 155,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Shut up, Kumashi! {Gotta change everywhere the name to \"Bearsy\", or whatever one we're choosing for him.}"
 },
 {
  "i": 156,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "What's with that look?! I hate it when you do that! {She doesn't ask, but in English you'd probably put a question mark on the 1st phrase.}"
 },
 {
  "i": 157,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Kumashi",
  "text": "I-I'm sorry."
 },
 {
  "i": 158,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "If you're not cute then you're not fit to serve me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 159,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guys",
  "text": "Hurry! Hurry!"
 },
 {
  "i": 160,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guys",
  "text": "It's starting! It's starting!"
 },
 {
  "i": 161,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guys",
  "text": "It's time for the night attack!"
 },
 {
  "i": 162,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guys",
  "text": "It's midnight!"
 },
 {
  "i": 163,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guys",
  "text": "Master!"
 },
 {
  "i": 164,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guys",
  "text": "Moriah-sama!"
 },
 {
  "i": 165,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guys",
  "text": "It's time to get up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 166,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guys",
  "text": "Nin! Do it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 167,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nin",
  "text": "Alright! Wake up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 168,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guys",
  "text": "Master!"
 },
 {
  "i": 169,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "I was having a nightmare!"
 },
 {
  "i": 170,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guys",
  "text": "Isn't that the best, Master?"
 },
 {
  "i": 171,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guys",
  "text": "Since Moriah-sama has been sleeping since the last time we had a night attack four days ago..."
 },
 {
  "i": 172,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guy",
  "text": "We've prepared you four days worth of food!"
 },
 {
  "i": 173,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guy",
  "text": "The prey this time is pretty tough!"
 },
 {
  "i": 174,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guy",
  "text": "It's the group that brought down Enies Lobby last month..."
 },
 {
  "i": 175,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guy",
  "text": "Straw Hat Luffy's crew!"
 },
 {
  "i": 176,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Guy",
  "text": "They'll certainly be of use to Moriah-sama!"
 },
 {
  "i": 177,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "It's really starting to pour..."
 },
 {
  "i": 178,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Alright, should we just run to the mansion then?"
 },
 {
  "i": 179,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Wait a sec!"
 },
 {
  "i": 180,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "I can see some huge thing behind the mansion."
 },
 {
  "i": 181,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "It looks like a mark..."
 },
 {
  "i": 182,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "The fog is clearing up a bit..."
 },
 {
  "i": 183,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Huh? A flag?"
 },
 {
  "i": 184,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "No."
 },
 {
  "i": 185,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Isn't that a sail?"
 },
 {
  "i": 186,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "All",
  "text": "A sail?"
 },
 {
  "i": 187,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "That's right!"
 },
 {
  "i": 188,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "All",
  "text": "You were still following us?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 189,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "It's just as he said, that's a sail."
 },
 {
  "i": 190,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "Thriller Bark..."
 },
 {
  "i": 191,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "Is not an island, but the largest pirate ship in the world!"
 },
 {
  "i": 192,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "You can see that at the back of the mansion is the main mast."
 },
 {
  "i": 193,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Old Man",
  "text": "That's where Gekko Moriah is!"
 },
 {
  "i": 194,
  "style": "Captions",
  "name": "Sign",
  "text": "{\\fad(600,200)}Soldier Zombie & General Zombie\\NGeneral"
 },
 {
  "i": 195,
  "style": "Captions",
  "name": "",
  "text": "{\\fad(200,0)}Absalom of the Graveyard"
 },
 {
  "i": 196,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Now, Soldier Zombie Unit..."
 },
 {
  "i": 197,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "The General Zombies will finish off the pirates!"
 },
 {
  "i": 198,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "{\\an8}No matter how many times you go down, just get back up quickly and crush them with fear of the undead!"
 },
 {
  "i": 199,
  "style": "Captions",
  "name": "Sign",
  "text": "{\\fad(600,200)}Wild Zombie & Surprise Zombie\\NGeneral"
 },
 {
  "i": 200,
  "style": "Captions",
  "name": "",
  "text": "{\\fad(200,875)}Ghost Princess\\NPerona"
 },
 {
  "i": 201,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Just now, the bell chimed."
 },
 {
  "i": 202,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Now it's time for us to really go at it."
 },
 {
  "i": 203,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Don't think you can escape from here, moronic pirates!"
 },
 {
  "i": 204,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Is everything ready?! Zombies!"
 },
 {
  "i": 205,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "This is the realm of the undead..."
 },
 {
  "i": 206,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Thriller Bark!"
 },
 {
  "i": 207,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Be prepared to witness a nightmare!"
 },
 {
  "i": 208,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Well, let's go!"
 },
 {
  "i": 209,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Into the haunted house!"
 },
 {
  "i": 210,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "How is this zombie research, Hogback?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 211,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "You were experimenting here!\\NYou've been resurrecting the dead, haven't you!?"
 },
 {
  "i": 212,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "H-Hey, Nami, saying it so bluntly..."
 },
 {
  "i": 213,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "From here on you're free to think whatever you like!"
 },
 {
  "i": 214,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "But what would make you think something like that?"
 },
 {
  "i": 215,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "I've seen that woman's obituary."
 },
 {
  "i": 216,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Victoria Cindry,"
 },
 {
  "i": 217,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "ten years ago, you died!"
 },
 {
  "i": 218,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "You guys! You went into that room?"
 },
 {
  "i": 219,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Cindry-chan!"
 },
 {
  "i": 220,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Samurai Ryuuma..."
 },
 {
  "i": 221,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Cast these fools into a world of shadows, immediately!"
 },
 {
  "i": 222,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "W-Wait!"
 },
 {
  "i": 223,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Into that shadow world where you will never see the light again!"
 },
 {
  "i": 224,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "The night attack has already begun!"
 },
 {
  "i": 225,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Ryuuma",
  "text": "Well, well! Now that I can see you clearly, you're quite a lovely woman."
 },
 {
  "i": 226,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Ryuuma",
  "text": "Beautiful!"
 },
 {
  "i": 227,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Ryuuma",
  "text": "Would you please allow me to see your panties?"
 },
 {
  "i": 228,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "As if!"
 },
 {
  "i": 229,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "This conversation...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 230,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "It's exactly like with him!"
 },
 {
  "i": 231,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "The zombies you've seen up until now were on a different level."
 },
 {
  "i": 232,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "He is a general zombie, and his body is special."
 },
 {
  "i": 233,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "This man came from \\NWano Country in the New World."
 },
 {
  "i": 234,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "You may think I'm just exaggerating, but the story of how he cut down a dragon mid-flight is still told."
 },
 {
  "i": 235,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "He's a legendary samurai."
 },
 {
  "i": 236,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "This is bad!"
 },
 {
  "i": 237,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Don't come!"
 },
 {
  "i": 238,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "There's no way to escape!"
 },
 {
  "i": 239,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Ryuuma",
  "text": "Cindry-san?"
 },
 {
  "i": 240,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Ryuuma",
  "text": "Could you please open up the door to that passage over there?"
 },
 {
  "i": 241,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Ryuuma",
  "text": "Also, I would love to have dinner afterwards."
 },
 {
  "i": 242,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "W-What? I thought he was going to cut us..."
 },
 {
  "i": 243,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "That scared me! What was he trying to do?"
 },
 {
  "i": 244,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "W-Whatever, it doesn't matter right now! Now's our chance to run, the door is wide open!"
 },
 {
  "i": 245,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Hurry!"
 },
 {
  "i": 246,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Well done."
 },
 {
  "i": 247,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "That's truly a master's swordplay. After humming and walking three blocks..."
 },
 {
  "i": 248,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hogback",
  "text": "Only then do they truly realize they've been cut..."
 },
 {
  "i": 249,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Move Name",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Three-Pace Hum:"
 },
 {
  "i": 250,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Ryuuma",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Notch Slash!"
 },
 {
  "i": 251,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Anybody home?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 252,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Pardon us!"
 },
 {
  "i": 253,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Just go in!"
 },
 {
  "i": 254,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "It's locked from..."
 },
 {
  "i": 255,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Oh, it's open."
 },
 {
  "i": 256,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "What're you calling \"open\", idiot..."
 },
 {
  "i": 257,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Hey! Is anyone home?"
 },
 {
  "i": 258,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Gekko Moriah!"
 },
 {
  "i": 259,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Is that all there is to this mansion? Not even a single servant around?"
 },
 {
  "i": 260,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "What's with this room? It looks like there's just been a fight."
 },
 {
  "i": 261,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "It can't be, Nami-san was involved...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 262,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "You have a lot of guts to wander this far, knowing our master's name."
 },
 {
  "i": 263,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Eh?! There's a pig growing out of the wall."
 },
 {
  "i": 264,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "Let's welcome our guests!"
 },
 {
  "i": 265,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Hey, hey, are these zombies too?"
 },
 {
  "i": 266,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "It seems whatever it is, on this island it's bound to be unusual."
 },
 {
  "i": 267,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Where are you..."
 },
 {
  "i": 268,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "hiding Nami-san!?"
 },
 {
  "i": 269,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "It's un-ladylike to open your mouth that much."
 },
 {
  "i": 270,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "Even if you're quite pretty."
 },
 {
  "i": 271,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "ZombieWoman",
  "text": "Eh? Really?"
 },
 {
  "i": 272,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "But you ruined it already once you leapt out of the picture frame."
 },
 {
  "i": 273,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Twist!"
 },
 {
  "i": 274,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "ZombieRound",
  "text": "The spear broke!"
 },
 {
  "i": 275,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "ZombieRound",
  "text": "What's with his body?! Is he iron!?"
 },
 {
  "i": 276,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "ZombieRound",
  "text": "S-Stop it! What are you?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 277,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "ZombieRound",
  "text": "Aren't you one of those other weaklings' friends?"
 },
 {
  "i": 278,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Two Sword Style:"
 },
 {
  "i": 279,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,0)}Double Slice."
 },
 {
  "i": 280,
  "style": "Note",
  "name": "Translation Note",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,0)}Rice"
 },
 {
  "i": 281,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "ZombieHungry",
  "text": "Rice? Sounds delicious!"
 },
 {
  "i": 282,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,0)}Flash!"
 },
 {
  "i": 283,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "ZombieHungry",
  "text": "It was awful!"
 },
 {
  "i": 284,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "This island is really fun!"
 },
 {
  "i": 285,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rugbear",
  "text": "You! You nimble, little bastard!"
 },
 {
  "i": 286,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "If you hadn't gotten in our way, we probably would've gotten along!"
 },
 {
  "i": 287,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,0)}Rubber..."
 },
 {
  "i": 288,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Bazooka!"
 },
 {
  "i": 289,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "R-Rugbear!"
 },
 {
  "i": 290,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Alright, all done."
 },
 {
  "i": 291,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "Oh, you're talking about those three!"
 },
 {
  "i": 292,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "They're fast asleep in the bedroom right now."
 },
 {
  "i": 293,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "Aren't you glad?"
 },
 {
  "i": 294,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "They're safe!"
 },
 {
  "i": 295,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Like we'd believe that crap."
 },
 {
  "i": 296,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "But it's true! Go see for yourself! It's the passage just up those stairs!"
 },
 {
  "i": 297,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Hey, wait a sec..."
 },
 {
  "i": 298,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "The curly-brow cook is gone..."
 },
 {
  "i": 299,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Huh? He was here just a second ago..."
 },
 {
  "i": 300,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Where did Sanji go off to?"
 },
 {
  "i": 301,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombies",
  "text": "Hey, stop laughing! They'll hear you."
 },
 {
  "i": 302,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "They must've done something at some point."
 },
 {
  "i": 303,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "We've lost an important man."
 },
 {
  "i": 304,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Hey, you.."
 },
 {
  "i": 305,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "But still, he's right. Sanji should be alright."
 },
 {
  "i": 306,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "But in this zombie mansion, we should focus on rescuing the other three, shouldn't we?"
 },
 {
  "i": 307,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "You all... just because you're a little stronger, don't get cocky..."
 },
 {
  "i": 308,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "Now that you've lost a friend, you'll show your true colours! Just look!"
 },
 {
  "i": 309,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "Anyways, it seems we have no other choice but to go cautiously."
 },
 {
  "i": 310,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "Hey, you guys! Really-"
 },
 {
  "i": 311,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "I don't think these kids' stories were true."
 },
 {
  "i": 312,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "In that case, let's take this pig with us as a guide."
 },
 {
  "i": 313,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie1",
  "text": "Go on, go!"
 },
 {
  "i": 314,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oinkchuck",
  "text": "Wait, you..."
 },
 {
  "i": 315,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie2",
  "text": "It'll do you good to learn how fearsome our master is."
 },
 {
  "i": 316,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie3",
  "text": "Our real boss is one of the Royal Seven Warlords of the Sea Gekko Mori-"
 },
 {
  "i": 317,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie3",
  "text": "I can't say it! It makes my soul freeze over!"
 },
 {
  "i": 318,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie4",
  "text": "Wah, it's bloodcurdling just saying that name!"
 },
 {
  "i": 319,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie5",
  "text": "Your missing friends are in trouble."
 },
 {
  "i": 320,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie5",
  "text": "One, then another. Your friends will slowly disappear."
 },
 {
  "i": 321,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie5",
  "text": "You should turn back."
 },
 {
  "i": 322,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie5",
  "text": "But before one of the Seven Warlords of the Sea Gekko-"
 },
 {
  "i": 323,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie5",
  "text": "No, {\\i1}our master's{\\i0} true might, the terror will keep you from saving anyone!"
 },
 {
  "i": 324,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Shut up and stop babbling."
 },
 {
  "i": 325,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Then tell that idiot Moriah this!"
 },
 {
  "i": 326,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "If anything happens to my crew..."
 },
 {
  "i": 327,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "I'll knock him off the face of this island!"
 },
 {
  "i": 328,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
